  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , Li et al. applied network coding to a deterministic broadcast approach called partial dominating pruning (PDP) [CITATION_2] in a multiple-source broadcast application. They proved that using only XOR operation, the coding algorithm is NP-complete and developed a greedy XOR-based approach for simplicity. The Reed-Solomon code was exploited to design an optimal Reed-Solomon code-based algorithm.",
